<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3896822>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Strict consensus tree of morphology-based parsimony analysis of species belonging to the former subtribe Periclystina (ingroup, names in black), and outgroups (names in red). Former Glenoleon species are shown on blue branches, former Austrogymnocnemia species on green branches. Numbers above branches are Bremer support values; numbers below branches are bootstrap values (shown where>50%)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3896822/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3897018>
    dc:description "FIGURE 99. Megagonoleon cardaleae: a) head, anterior; b) head and thorax, dorsal; c) wings, dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3897018/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3897020>
    dc:description "FIGURE 100. Megagonoleon cardaleae: male: a) terminalia, lateral; b) genitalia, lateral; c) genitalia, posterior; female: d) terminalia, lateral; e) 7th sternite and pregenital plate, ventral. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3897020/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3897022>
